        <h3>Sandra Bullock  </h3>
        <small>
            Actor
        </small>
    </div>
            <div class="baseball-card">
    <div class="header"></div>
    <div class="middle">
        <h2>Sandra Bullock</h2>
        <div class="bc-content">
            <img width="160" height="120" src="http://thedailyshow.mtvnimages.com/images/shows/tds/videos/season_12_v/batch2/tds_celeb_12036_a_v6.jpg?width=160&amp;height=120&amp;quality=0.91&amp;crop=true" alt="" />
            Sandra Bullock is an Oscar-winning actress. Her latest film is "Gravity," a thriller set in space that co-stars George Clooney. Since her breakthrough performance in the action thriller "Speed" (1994), Bullock has appeared in a long list of feature films including "The Net" (1995), "A Time to Kill" (1996), "Forces of Nature" (1999), and "Miss Congeniality" (2000). In 2009, Bullock won the Academy Award for Best Performance by an Actress in a Leading Role for her performance in "The Blind Side."
        </div>
